Telkom has unveiled its Big Deal for March 2019. The package offers users LTE and Wi-Fi data, along with a Huawei MiFi router. Huawei’s MiFi router can connect up to 10 devices at once and handle download speeds of 150Mbps, and is powered by a 1,500mAh battery. Telkom added that out-of-bundle rates of R0.30 per MB apply for additional data usage. Telkom said the deal is available until 31 March 2019, or while stocks last. <span data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;" class="mce_SELRES_start">﻿</span>